      <title>随着危机逐渐消退，北欧房东着眼于 2025 年欧元债券复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/nordic-landlords-eye-2025-euro-bond-revival-as-crunch-fades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年秋天，随着 Heimstaden Bostad AB 和 Castellum AB 发行债券，欧洲企业债券市场结束了为期两年的融资紧缩局面，到 2025 年，欧洲企业债券市场可能会迎来更多来自北欧房东的债券发行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/nordic-landlords-eye-2025-euro-bond-revival-as-crunch-fades</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 09:36:49 GMT</pubDate>
