    <item>
      <title>零星散货：吉姆·卡隆谈美联储的历史性调整（播客）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/audio/2024-12-20/morgan-stanley-s-jim-caron-on-the-fed-s-historic-adjustment-odd-lots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，美联储一如预期降息 25 个基点。但美联储也上调了 2025 年通胀预期，并预计明年只会再降息两次。市场对此反应激烈，主要指标创下长期以来最糟糕的一天。更重要的是，市场无处可藏。债券和黄金也与股票一起遭到抛售。那么现在发生了什么？这对投资组合构建意味着什么？在本期节目中，我们采访了首席投资官 Jim Caron]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/audio/2024-12-20/morgan-stanley-s-jim-caron-on-the-fed-s-historic-adjustment-odd-lots</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市料创九月以来最大单周跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/european-stocks-set-for-the-biggest-weekly-slide-since-september</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者担心美国关税威胁，并准备迎接美联储更为强硬的利率立场，欧洲股市连续第二天下跌，有望创下三个多月来最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/european-stocks-set-for-the-biggest-weekly-slide-since-september</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 08:12:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国借款额将超过预期，这对里夫斯来说是个新问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/uk-posts-smaller-than-forecast-budget-deficit-as-debt-costs-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府借款今年可能会超过官方预测，这增加了财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 明年初必须再次寻求更多资金的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/uk-posts-smaller-than-forecast-budget-deficit-as-debt-costs-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 07:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券热潮升温，中国短期债券收益率跌至二十年来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-one-year-yield-sinks-toward-1-as-policy-easing-bets-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受押注激进放松政策和避险资产需求推动，中国一年期债券收益率突破全球金融危机时期的水平，降至二十多年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-one-year-yield-sinks-toward-1-as-policy-easing-bets-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 01:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
